<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <%- include('../includes/head.ejs') %>
    <body>
        <%- include('../includes/header.ejs') %>
        <%- include('../includes/menu.ejs') %>
        <%- include('../includes/loading.ejs') %>
        <div id="myprofile-container">
            <section class="photo-box">
                <img src=<%= myProfile.photo %>>
                <button type="button" id="photo" name="photo">
                    <i class="fa-regular fa-pen-to-square fa-lg"></i>
                </button>
                <p><span id="client"><%= myProfile.name %></span>님, 환영 합니다.</p>
            </section>
            <section class="myprofile">
                <ul>
                    <li id="comment"><p>계정 관리</p><span>내 정보를 관리할 수 있습니다.</span></li>
                    <li>이메일<p id="email"><%= myProfile.email %></p></li>
                    <li id="name">이름<p><%= myProfile.name %><i class="fa-regular fa-pen-to-square"></i></p></li>
                    <li id="unique-id">고유아이디<p><%= myProfile.uniqueId %><i class="fa-regular fa-clone"></i></p></li>
                    <li id="phone">핸드폰 번호<p><%= myProfile.phone %><i class="fa-regular fa-pen-to-square"></i></p></li>
                    <li id="auth-check">인증 여부<p>인증 안됨<i class="fa-regular fa-pen-to-square"></i></p></li>
                    <li id="sns">연결된 SNS
                        <div class="logo-box">
                            <% if(myProfile.snsAccount.isOAuth) { %>
                                <img src="<%= myProfile.snsAccount.logoImageUrl %>" id="sns-logo">
                                <%= myProfile.snsAccount.company %>
                            <% } else { %>
                                <p>연결 안됨</p>
                            <% } %>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>
            <section class="myprofile">
                <ul>
                    <li id="comment"><p>개인 정보</p><span>개인 정보를 안전하게 보관할 수 있습니다.</span></li>
                    <li id="withdrawal">회원탈퇴<p><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right-from-bracket"></i></p></li>
                </ul>
            </section>
        </div>		
        <%- include('../includes/script.ejs') %>
    </body>
</html>